    "The International Organization for Standardization (ISO) provides various standards for security requirements related to the maintenance of information security management systems and risk management.",
    "The Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act (HIPPA) is important for organizations that handle healthcare data such as hospitals, insurance companies, etc.",
    "The General Data Protection Act (GDPR) is important for businesses operating in Europe as it regulates the data protection of the citizens of the European Union.",
    "Payment Card Industry Data Security Standard (PCI-DSS) is a set of regulations for reducing credit card-related fraud and applies to companies handling credit card information.",
    "In this feature, we evaluate which compliance standards are satisfied by the studied SIEM systems."
